NACL+ H2SO4= NASO4+ HCL: nacl is sodium chloride and H2SO4 is sulphuric acid and naso4 fro sodium sulphate and HCL hydro chloric acid:

when you pass HCL with dry litmus then there will be no change:
but when you pass HCL(G) to moist litmus it turns the blue litmus red:
